get.description: Search for property records in a geographical area, or by a specific address.

parameters.name: address
parameters.description: The **full address** of the property, in the format `Street, City, State, Zip`. Used to retrieve data for a specific property, or together with the `radius` parameter to search for properties in a circular area

schema.default: 5500 Grand Lake Dr, San Antonio, TX, 78244

parameters.name: city
parameters.description: The name of the city, used to search for properties in a specific city. This parameter is case-sensitive

parameters.name: state
parameters.description: The 2-character state abbreviation, used to search for properties in a specific state. This parameter is case-sensitive

parameters.name: zipCode
parameters.description: The 5-digit zip code, used to search for properties in a specific zip code

parameters.name: latitude
parameters.description: The latitude of the search area. Use the `latitude`/`longitude` and `radius` parameters to search for properties in a circular area

parameters.name: longitude
parameters.description: The longitude of the search area. Use the `latitude`/`longitude` and `radius` parameters to search for properties in a circular area

parameters.name: radius
parameters.description: The radius of the search area in miles, with a maximum of 100. Use in combination with the `latitude`/`longitude` or `address` parameters to search for properties in a circular area

parameters.name: propertyType
parameters.description: The type of the property, used to search for properties matching this criteria. See [explanation of property types](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/property-types). Supports [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: bedrooms
parameters.description: The number of bedrooms, used to search for properties matching this criteria. Use `0` to indicate a studio layout. Supports [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters) and [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: bathrooms
parameters.description: The number of bathrooms, used to search for properties matching this criteria. Supports fractions to indicate partial bathrooms, [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters) and [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: squareFootage
parameters.description: The total living area size in square feet, used to search for properties matching this criteria. Supports [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters) and [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: lotSize
parameters.description: The total lot size in square feet, used to search for properties matching this criteria. Supports [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters) and [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: yearBuilt
parameters.description: The year of construction, used to search for properties matching this criteria. Supports [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters) and [multiple values](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-multiple-value-parameters)

parameters.name: saleDateRange
parameters.description: The number of days since a property was last sold, with a minimum of 1. Used to search for properties that were sold within the specified date range. Supports [numeric ranges](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/search-queries#using-numeric-range-parameters)

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: The maximum number of property records to return, between 1 and 500. Defaults to `50` if not provided. [Learn more](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/pagination) about pagination

parameters.name: offset
parameters.description: The index of the first property record to return, used to paginate through large lists of results. Defaults to `0` if not provided. [Learn more](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/pagination) about pagination

parameters.name: includeTotalCount
parameters.description: When enabled, will return the total number of results matching the current query in the `X-Total-Count` response header. Defaults to `false` if not provided

get.description: Returns a property value estimate and comparable properties.

parameters.name: address
parameters.description: The **full address** of the property, in the format `Street, City, State, Zip`. You need to provide either the `address` or the `latitude`/`longitude` parameters

schema.default: 5500 Grand Lake Dr, San Antonio, TX, 78244

parameters.name: latitude
parameters.description: The latitude of the property. The `latitude`/`longitude` can be provided instead of the `address` parameter

parameters.name: longitude
parameters.description: The longitude of the property. The `latitude`/`longitude` can be provided instead of the `address` parameter

parameters.name: propertyType
parameters.description: The type of the property. See [explanation of property types](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/property-types)

parameters.name: bedrooms
parameters.description: The number of bedrooms in the property. Use `0` to indicate a studio layout

parameters.name: bathrooms
parameters.description: The number of bathrooms in the property. Supports fractions to indicate partial bathrooms

parameters.name: squareFootage
parameters.description: The total living area size of the property, in square feet

parameters.name: maxRadius
parameters.description: The maximum distance between comparable listings and the subject property, in miles

parameters.name: daysOld
parameters.description: The maximum number of days since comparable listings were last seen on the market, with a minimum of 1

parameters.name: compCount
parameters.description: The number of comparable listings to use when calculating the value estimate, between 5 and 25. Defaults to `15` if not provided

parameters.name: lookupSubjectAttributes
parameters.description: When enabled, will attempt to look up subject property attributes to find more relevant comps. Defaults to `true` if not provided. [Learn more](https://developers.rentcast.io/reference/property-valuation#subject-property-attribute-lookup) about this feature
